The inauguration ceremony of the Retd. Brigadier Julius Maada Bio as the President of Sierra Leone took place Saturday, May 12 at the national stadium in Freetown. World leaders, diplomats and celebrities present at the special occasion includes President George Wear of Liberia, President Faure Gnassingb√© of Togo, Vice President of Nigeria Professor Osibajo, Omotola Jalade-Ekeinde, Mercy Johnson, Mr Ibu and First Lady of The Gambia. Her Excellency Fatima Jabbe-Bio is now the new First Lady of Sierra Leone.   